  "instructions": [
    "In a small bowl, combine the yeast, 1 tablespoon of the butter, and 1 tablespoon of the chicken broth. Let it sit for 5-10 minutes, until it becomes frothy.",
    "Add the yeast mixture, feta cheese, kefir cheese, oregano, thyme, garlic, salt, and pepper to the ceramic tagine.",
    "Mix well to combine.",
    "Add 1 cup of the braising liquid and put the lid on the tagine.",
    "Cook over low heat for 20 minutes, then increase the heat to medium-low and cook for another 10 minutes.",
    "After 30 minutes, remove the lid and let the cheese pull for 5 minutes.",
    "Garnish with parsley and mint, and serve hot.",
    "Let it rest for 5 minutes before slicing and serving."
  ],
